"I screw up alot
command! W w
command! Wq wq
command! Q q
command! WQ wq

"flop the background from light->dark or vv.
nmap <silent> <C-g> <ESC>:BG<CR>

"match key as % sucks
nmap  <leader>m %
nmap  <leader>f zf%

"insert a 'debugger' on the line above the current
nmap <silent> <leader>db Odebugger; 9001<ESC>=jj

"insert a 'binding.pry' on the line above the current
nmap <silent> <leader>r<space> Obinding.pry<ESC>=jj

"remap nerdtree toggler from the default
nmap <silent> <leader>d<space> :execute 'NERDTreeToggle '. getcwd()<CR>
unmap <leader>d

"remap mark from ` to ', and vice versa, so we get the better behavior more
"easily.
nnoremap ' `
nnoremap ` '


nmap <silent> <leader>a<space> :Ack <cword><CR>

nmap <silent> F :cnext<CR>
nmap <silent> B :cprevious<CR>

nmap <silent> <leader>b<space> :BuffergatorToggle<CR>


